    "outline_title": "kev pom Organizer",
    "outline_text": "Tsim kev pom representations ntawm koj cov ntsiab's structure. Transform cov ntawv into 6 different graphic organizer hom, txhua tailored mus tshwj xeeb thinking thiab reasoning cov qauv.\n### phab ntsa kev xaiv\n• **Structure Type**: Xaiv koj organizer hom los ntawm 6 muaj types.\n• **Custom cov lus qhia**: Ntxiv tshwj xeeb guidance rau tailored organization (e.g., \"focus rau saum cause chains\" los yog \"siv these tshwj xeeb lo lus\").\n### Organizer Types\n• **Venn duab piav qhia**: Sib piv thiab contrast two los yog ntau lub tswv yim nrog draggable tshooj.\n• **Structured Outline**: Hierarchical daim ntawv teev npe qhia main ideas thiab supporting kev meej.\n• **Key Lub tswv yim Map**: Spider-web visualization connecting central ideas mus related lub tswv yim.\n• **Flow chart**: Visualize sequential processes, timelines, los yog decision trees.\n• **Cause thiab Effect**: Fishbone/Ishikawa duab piav qhia qhia relationships nyob nruab nrab factors thiab outcomes.\n• **Problem Solution**: Txheeb xyuas cov teeb meem, tshuaj xyuas contributing factors, thiab propose solutions.\n### Interactive cov yam ntxwv\n• **Rub-thiab-Tso Sorting**: tub ntxhais kawm tshais yam nyob nruab nrab Venn tshooj los yog reorder outline lub tshoj.\n• **kev ua si hom**: Convert static organizers into competitive sorting activities.\n• **Kho hom**: Rename headings, ntxiv sub-lub tshoj, los yog restructure cov ntsiab manually.\n• **ob hom lus hom**: Saib organizers nrog translated labels rau multilingual cov tub ntxhais kawm.\n### Pro cov lus qhia Siv Cause & Effect organizers rau science kev sim thiab Problem Solution rau persuasive sau ntawv assignments.\n### UDL Connection\n• **Representation**: Guides processing thiab visualization (Guideline 3.3) by transforming linear cov ntawv into spatial relationships.",
    "visual_title": "AI kev pom",
    "visual_text": "Enhance kev nkag siab nrog AI-tau tsim imagery. Tsim kev pom representations ntawm key lub tswv yim siv diverse art hom thiab intelligent layout hom mus kev txhawb Dual Coding tswv yim.\n### phab ntsa kev xaiv\n• **Worksheet hom**: Creates fill-hauv--blank hom kev pom rau tub ntxhais kawm activities.\n• **Enhanced kev pom**: Uses creative logic rau ntau artistic, tsawg literal interpretations.\n• **cov ntawv Reduced**: Generates pure kev pom without labels los yog captions mus reduce cognitive nqa los.\n• **Layout hom**: Direct AI Art Director mus tsim Single duab, Before/After Comparisons, cov theem-by-cov theem Sequences, los yog Labeled duab piav qhia.\n• **Art hom**: Xaiv los ntawm default, Isometric, Pixel Art, Watercolor, Blueprint, Comic, kab Art, los yog 3D Render.\n• **Custom cov lus qhia**: Describe tshwj xeeb kev pom requirements los yog constraints.\n### Interactive cov yam ntxwv\n• **Regenerate**: Request tshiab variation nrog one nyem.\n• **Rub los**: Khaws siab-quality duab rau slides los yog handouts.\n• **Lwv**: Tshem thiab pib fresh yog tias needed.\n### Pro cov lus qhia Siv \"Sequence\" layout hom nrog \"kab Art\" hom mus instantly tsim printable multi-cov theem instructional guides!\n### UDL Connection\n• **Representation**: Clarify syntax thiab structure (Guideline 2) by providing kev pom alternatives mus cov ntawv.",
