    "quiz_title": "Gamified kev sim",
    "quiz_text": "Gamified kev ntsuam xyuas nrog multiple competitive thiab immersive hom. los ntawm ncaj qha chav kawm battles mus puzzle-based escape rooms.\n### kev ua si hom\n• **Ncaj qha kev sim**: Real-time synchronized kev sib ntsib nrog qhab nia trackings thiab kev sib ntsib codes rau tub ntxhais kawm mus join.\n• **Team Showdown**: Team-based competition nrog xim-coded groups thiab collaborative scoring.\n• **Boss Battle**: chav kawm vs AI boss•lo lus teb correctly mus deal damage thiab defeat boss together!\n• **Escape Room**: Immersive themed puzzles nrog cov lus qhia, ciphers, locked doors, thiab final escape kev sib tw.\n• **Review hom**: Tus kheej-paced xyaum nrog immediate feedback.\n### lo lus nug Types\n• **Multiple Choice**: tus qauv MCQ nrog configurable lo lus nug suav.\n• **Reflection lo lus nug**: Qhib-ended responses rau deeper thinking.\n• **Fill-hauv--Blank**: Ua kom tiav kab lus nrog missing key lo lus.\n• **Matching**: Connect related lub tswv yim.\n• **Cipher Puzzles**: Decode encrypted cov xov hauv Escape Room hom.\n### Gamification cov yam ntxwv\n• **Leaderboards**: Real-time ranking during ncaj qha kev sib ntsib.\n• **Team xim**: Auto-assigned team identities rau group competitions.\n• **cov lus qhia system**: Spend cov lus qhia tokens rau clues hauv Escape Room (limited supply!).\n• **Kev ua tiav Kev tshawb**: Track escape room completions thiab kev sim qhab nia across kev sib ntsib.\n### AI Auto-Grader\n• **Reflection Grading**: AI evaluates qhib-ended lo lus teb nrog rubric-based feedback.\n• **Instant qhab nia**: ua nws tus kheej scoring nrog personalized feedback rau txhua response.\n### Ncaj qha Differentiated Delivery\n• **Group Overrides**: Assign different kev pab cuam los yog hom lus version mus tshwj xeeb tub ntxhais kawm groups mid-kev sib ntsib.\n• **Targeted Push**: Xa scaffolded kev sim mus Tier 3 tub ntxhais kawm while rest work rau saum tus qauv material.\n• **Real-Time Switching**: Tsis yog need mus end kev sib ntsib•differentiate rau saum fly los ntawm xib fwb dashboard.\n### xib fwb cov yam ntxwv\n• **Presentation hom**: Project lo lus nug fullscreen rau whole-chav kawm discussion.\n• **kev sib ntsib Codes**: Tsim join codes rau tub ntxhais kawm mus connect los ntawm any device.\n• **Qhia/Zais lo lus teb**: Hloov lo lus teb key visibility during review.\n• **DOK theem**: Align lo lus nug mus tob ntawm Knowledge tus qauv.\n### Pro cov lus qhia Siv Escape Room hom mus boost engagement•tub ntxhais kawm daws teeb meem puzzles mus 'escape' while demonstrating cov ntsiab mastery.\n### UDL Connection\n• **Engagement**: Optimize kev sib tw (Guideline 8.2) dhau los ntawm incremental kev nyuaj thiab gamified feedback loops.",
