    "brainstorm_text": "Dual-purpose ideation thiab simulation generator. Tsim engagement hooks thiab activities OR tsim interactive Canvas simulations.\n### Ideation hom\n• **Custom cov lus qhia**: Ntxiv tshwj xeeb focus thaj av los yog context rau ideas.\n• **Real-World Connections**: Activities linking cov ntsiab mus careers thiab daily life.\n• **Discussion Hooks**: Provocative lo lus nug mus spark chav kawm conversations.\n• **Project-Based Ideas**: ntev-lo lus project lub tswv yim nrog driving lo lus nug.\n### Gemini Canvas (Simulation Generator) Tsim interactive Canvas simulations nrog iterative AI refinement:\n• **Simulation Types**: React feem, Python visualizations, Physics simulations, Custom chatbots.\n• **cov theem Suav Slider** (1-10): ntau cov theem = ntau refined cov lus qhia rau deeper exploration.\n• **Canvas Prompt pob nias**: Auto-launches Gemini Canvas nrog koj simulation code.\n### Tsim tau Idea daim npav txhua idea muaj:\n• **Title & Description**: Core activity overview.\n• **Connection Field**: yuav ua li cas it links mus koj cov ntsiab.\n• **xib fwb Guide**: Tsim cov theem-by-cov theem implementation cov lus qhia per idea.\n• **Kho hom**: Hloov any field after tiam.\n### Pro cov lus qhia Siv Python simulation hom mus tsim auto-graded lej xyaum cov cuab yeej•tub ntxhais kawm kev nkag tus nqi thiab get instant feedback!\n### UDL Connection\n• **Engagement**: Optimize relevance, tus nqi, thiab authenticity (Guideline 7) by connecting learning mus real-world cov teeb meem thiab interactive experiences.",
