    "persona_text": "Persona Interview hom brings cov ntsiab mus life dhau los ntawm immersive tus cwj pwm conversations. Interview historical figures, fictional tus cwj pwm, los yog AI-tau tsim experts hauv gamified experience qhov ntawd tsim empathy thiab deepens understanding.\n### Interview hom\n• **1-rau saum-1 Interview**: Deep conversation nrog single tus cwj pwm rau focused exploration.\n• **phab ntsa Discussion**: Xaiv multiple personas rau group debates thiab diverse perspectives.\n• **Free Response vs Multiple Choice**: Hloov nyob nruab nrab qhib-ended typing los yog guided lo lus nug kev xaiv.\n### Gamification cov yam ntxwv\n• **XP system**: Earn Interview XP rau quality lo lus nug thiab thoughtful engagement.\n• **lub cim**: Unlock achievements like *Harmonizer*, *thawj Insight*, *Rapport Builder*, thiab *Master Interviewer*.\n• **Reflection Grading**: Submit final reflection mus earn bonus XP nrog AI-powered feedback.\n• **nyuaj hom**: Kaw cov lus qhia rau extra kev sib tw thiab higher XP nqi zog.\n### suab & Kev nkag mus tau\n• **Auto-Nyeem**: Personas hais their responses aloud siv cov ntawv-mus-Speech.\n• **Auto-Xa**: Hands-free hom automatically sends koj cov xov after pause.\n• **Custom cov lus qhia**: duab persona's background, era, los yog expertise theem.\n### Pro cov lus qhia\n• Project Persona kev sib tham rau saum board thiab muaj whole chav kawm vote rau saum dab tsi lo lus nug mus ask tom ntej.\n### UDL Connection\n• **Engagement**: Foster collaboration thiab community (Guideline 8) dhau los ntawm simulated social learning interactions.",
