    "header_ai_backend": "AI Backend Kev Teeb Tsa: Hloov los yog xaiv koj preferred AI provider globally (e.g., Google Gemini, Anthropic Claude, OpenAI, los yog local Ollama). Qhov no dictates which model handles nyuaj NLP tasks thiab cov ncauj lus tiam across tag nrho cov cuab yeej.",
