    "source_link_btn": "Coj los cov ntsiab directly los ntawm web pages. Muab tso any URL mus rho tawm: main article cov ntawv (ads thiab navigation removed), duab nrog captions, thiab embedded media descriptions. Ua hauj lwm nrog: news articles, Wikipedia, educational sites, blog posts, thiab most public web pages. AI intelligently identifies main cov ntsiab thaj av, ignoring sidebars thiab footers. Rau paywalled cov ntsiab, only freely pom tau cov ntawv yog extracted. YouTube URLs rho tawm video transcripts thaum muaj. Imported cov ntsiab becomes koj qhov chaw material rau tag nrho tiam cov cuab yeej. cov lus qhia: Verify extracted cov ntsiab matches thawj—layout differences may affect extraction.",
