    "brainstorm_simulation_detailed": "Tsim interactive simulations rau hands-rau saum learning. Simulation types: React feem (interactive UI elements tub ntxhais kawm tuaj yeem manipulate), Python Visualizations (cov ncauj lus chart, graph, thiab interactive plots), Physics Simulations (kev txav, lub zog, gravity, thiab collision demonstrations), thiab Chatbot (conversational AI rau roleplay thiab xyaum). txhua simulation runs hauv embedded environment. cov theem slider controls kev nyuaj: ntau cov theem = ntau sophisticated simulation nrog additional cov yam ntxwv. Simulations yog customized mus koj cov ncauj lus thiab learning objectives. Perfect rau: STEM lub tswv yim, cov ncauj lus literacy, thiab abstract idea visualization. Tsim tau code tuaj yeem be exported thiab modified yog tias desired.",
    "brainstorm_step_count_detailed": "Control yuav ua li cas many iterative refinement passes AI makes rau saum koj cov ntsiab. txhua cov theem adds tob thiab kev meej. ceev brainstorms (3-5 cov theem): ceev cov txiaj ntsig, zoo rau initial exploration, may be tsawg polished. tus qauv (6-8 cov theem): balanced quality thiab ceev, suitable rau most siv cases. Deep exploration (9-12 cov theem): maximum refinement, comprehensive kev tawm, takes longer. ntau cov theem mean AI has ntau chances mus: ntxiv kev meej, refine ideas, txheeb xyuas connections, thiab polish presentation. Consider muaj time thiab purpose thaum selecting. Rau time-sensitive planning, siv fewer cov theem; rau important deliverables, siv ntau. kev nce qib indicator qhia current cov theem during tiam.",
