    "concept_sort_input": "Define dab tsi cov ntsiab should be sorted. Sau topics like: Types ntawm rocks, Parts ntawm speech, feem thiab decimal, los yog Renewable vs. non-renewable. AI tsim sortable yam based rau saum koj cov ncauj lus. ntau tshwj xeeb topics yield ntau focused yam. AI draws los ntawm koj qhov chaw cov ntawv yog tias muaj rau curriculum kev sib raug. koj tuaj yeem daim ntawv teev npe tshwj xeeb yam mus suav nrog: Suav nrog igneous, sedite, sedimentary, thiab metamorphic. Cov ncauj lus should suggest natural pawg—yog tias pawg yog tsis obvious, hais kom meej them separately. Tiam tsim balanced pawg nrog similar tus lej ntawm yam per group.",
