    "timeline_topic_detailed": "Describe koj timeline cov ncauj lus nrog specificity. Strong piv txwv: American Revolution 1775-1783, Stages ntawm photosynthesis, Marie Curie biography, Civil Rights movement events. tshwj xeeb topics kev pab AI: txheeb xyuas sab xis events, xaiv appropriate date ranges, thiab suav nrog relevant kev meej. Rau historical timelines: suav nrog date range yog tias known. Rau process timelines: name process clearly. Rau biography: suav nrog person thiab focus thaj av. Vague topics like History los yog Science tsim generic cov txiaj ntsig. ntau tshwj xeeb koj cov ncauj lus, ntau accurate thiab useful koj timeline. cov lus qhia: Suav nrog theem qib kawm context yog tias cov ncauj lus spans kev nyuaj theem.",
    "timeline_count_detailed": "Teeb yuav ua li cas many events mus suav nrog hauv koj timeline. 5-8 events: concise overview, easier mus sequence, zoo rau introductions thiab ceev activities. 10-15 events: comprehensive coverage, ntau challenging sequencing, suitable rau meej study. Consider: tub ntxhais kawm age (younger = fewer events), time muaj (5 events = ceev activity), thiab tob needed (ntau events = ntau kev meej). AI xaiv most significant events yog tias fewer yog requested. ntau events take longer mus tsim. Sequencing kev nyuaj increases nrog suav. cov lus qhia: Pib nrog fewer events rau initial learning, then increase rau deeper exploration.",
