    "alignment_generate_button": "Khiav tus qauv kev sib raug analysis rau saum koj qhov chaw cov ntsiab. AI examines: cov lus, lub tswv yim, kev txawj, thiab ntsiab lus hauv koj cov ntsiab. kev tawm qhia: matched tus qauv nrog feem pua confidence, coverage gaps (tus qauv tsis addressed), thiab suggestions rau expanding coverage. Analysis takes 10-20 vib nas depending rau saum cov ntsiab ntev thiab tus qauv framework size. cov txiaj ntsig tuaj yeem be: exported rau zaj lus qhia planning documentation, added mus zaj lus qhia plans automatically, thiab shared nrog administrators rau curriculum mapping. Multiple tus qauv may match single piece ntawm cov ntsiab. Review matches rau qhov tseeb since AI kev sib raug yog suggestive, tsis definitive. cov lus qhia: Siv kev sib raug cov txiaj ntsig mus txheeb xyuas instructional gaps.",
