    "simplified_cloze_mode": "Convert any passage into cloze (fill-hauv--blank) reading activity. AI strategically removes cov lus lo lus, leaving blanks nrog lo lus banks. Three kev nyuaj theem: yooj yim (cov lus lo lus removed, lo lus bank provided), Medium (key lo lus removed, limited cov lus qhia), nyuaj (multiple lo lus removed, no bank). Tsim: cov lus hauv context, reading kev nkag siab, thiab prediction kev txawj. cov yam ntxwv auto-check nrog instant feedback, retry kev xaiv, thiab kev nce qib kev tshawb. Xa tawm as printable worksheet los yog assign as interactive digital activity. Perfect rau: cov lus kev ntsuam xyuas, reading kev nkag siab xyaum, thiab differentiated homework.",
    "simplified_scramble_game": "Convert any passage into interactive lo lus/kab lus unscrambling activity. tub ntxhais kawm pom scrambled lo lus los yog kab lus thiab rub elements into correct grammatical order. kev nyuaj theem: lo lus theem (unscramble letters within lo lus—tsim spelling), Phrase theem (arrange phrases within kab lus—tsim syntax awareness), kab lus theem (order kab lus hauv nqe lus—tsim coherence). cov yam ntxwv: rub-thiab-tso nrog touch kev txhawb, immediate feedback, retry kev xaiv, thiab cov lus qhia pob nias. Tsim: grammar intuition, kab lus structure awareness, thiab reading fluency. Zoo rau: grammar xyaum, editing kev txawj, thiab understanding yuav ua li cas lo lus order affects meaning. XP awarded rau correct arrangements.",
    "simplified_revise_mode": "Kev nkag qib siab editing cov cuab yeej rau fine-grained cov ntsiab manipulation. Only muaj hauv xib fwb Saib. cov yam ntxwv: Xaiv any cov ntawv span mus: rewrite at different reading theem, ntxiv/tshem supporting kev meej, simplify cov lus while preserving meaning, expand nrog piv txwv, los yog condense rau brevity. AI maintains coherence nrog surrounding cov ntawv. Siv rau: targeted differentiation (simplify one nqe lus rau sib tw reader group), cov ntsiab correction, thiab iterative refinement. Kev hloov tracked as version—revert anytime. Sib piv hom qhia thawj vs. revised side by side. Perfect rau tab tom tsim multiple version ntawm tib yam base cov ntsiab rau different learner groups.",
    "simplified_download_audio": "Khaws cov ntawv-mus-speech suab as downloadable cov ntaub ntawv. suab siv koj current suab kev teeb tsa (suab, ceev, volume). cov ntaub ntawv hom yog MP3 rau universal compatibility. Siv downloaded suab rau: offline listening xyaum, kev nkag mus tau accommodations, homework suab kev txhawb, thiab multimedia projects. cov ntaub ntawv muaj ua kom tiav cov ntawv as currently displayed. ntev cov ntawv may take moment mus tsim. Multiple version at different speeds tuaj yeem be downloaded. Zoo rau: listening homework, audiobook creation, thiab study cov khoom siv. cov lus qhia: Rub los at slower ceev rau sib tw readers, normal ceev rau fluent readers.",
    "simplified_complexity_slider": "Dynamic slider mus hloov reading theem instantly. Rub mus hloov kev nyuaj los ntawm yooj yim (qib 1) mus qib siab (qib 12+). cov ntawv regenerates at tshiab theem thaum koj release slider. Siv rau: ceev differentiation during chav kawm, finding appropriate kev sib tw theem, thiab comparing version. Slider kev hloov affect: cov lus, kab lus ntev, thiab lub tswv yim density. Moving slider regenerates cov ntsiab (takes 5-10 vib nas). Thawj qhov chaw yog preserved. Combine nrog Sib piv hom mus pom different theem side-by-side. cov lus qhia: Let tub ntxhais kawm kho their own reading theem mus tsim tus kheej-awareness ntawm reading ability thiab appropriate kev sib tw.",
    "simplified_overwrite_toggle": "Control version management thaum changing kev nyuaj. thaum ON (Overwrite): tshiab theem replaces current cov ntawv, single version maintained, cleaner workspace. thaum OFF (Tsim tshiab): txhua theem tsim separate version, multiple version muaj, yooj yim comparison. Overwrite hom yog simpler rau single-tub ntxhais kawm siv. Tsim tshiab hom helps nrog: differentiation preparation, version comparison, thiab maintaining multiple reading theem. version yog pom tau los ntawm version dropdown. Storage limits apply mus tus lej ntawm version. cov lus qhia: Siv Tsim tshiab thaum preparing differentiated cov khoom siv rau chav kawm, Overwrite thaum working nrog tus kheej tub ntxhais kawm.",
    "brainstorm_panel": "Tsim cross-curricular activity ideas qhov ntawd extend learning beyond screen. AI tsim suggestions rau: hands-rau saum projects, movement breaks, group discussions, art connections, real-world applications, thiab home extensions. txhua idea muaj: cov khoom siv needed, time estimate, learning objective kev sib raug, thiab cov theem-by-cov theem xib fwb guide. Perfect rau UDL Principle 3 (Multiple Means ntawm Engagement) by providing varied ways mus interact nrog cov ntsiab. Lim by: indoor/outdoor, tus kheej/group, STEM/humanities, low-prep/siab-impact. Zoo rau zaj lus qhia planning thiab differentiated learning stations.",
