    "persona_panel": "Engage hauv AI-powered conversations nrog historical figures, scientists, authors, los yog fictional tus cwj pwm. tub ntxhais kawm ask lo lus nug thiab txais responses hauv-tus cwj pwm based rau saum accurate historical/literary knowledge. cov yam ntxwv: Socratic hom (tus cwj pwm asks probing lo lus nug rov qab), reflection cov lus qhia after conversation, XP nqi zog rau quality lo lus nug, thiab conversation transcripts rau kev ntsuam xyuas. kev txhawb perspective-taking, primary qhov chaw analysis, thiab engagement nrog cov ntsiab. xib fwb tuaj yeem hloov raws siab nyiam tus cwj pwm knowledge thiab speaking hom. Zoo rau: history (interview Lincoln), science (talk mus Marie Curie), literature (kev sib tham nrog Atticus Finch).",
