    "header_settings": "Kev nkag main kev teeb tsa phab ntsa rau kev pom kev nkag mus tau thiab tso tawm preferences. kev teeb tsa suav nrog: Font Size (adjustable los ntawm 12px mus 24px), Font Family (suav nrog OpenDyslexic), Letter Spacing, kab siab, xim ntsiab lus (Light, Dark, Siab Contrast), xim Overlays (Blue, Peach, Yellow), thiab Bionic Reading hloov. tag nrho kev teeb tsa apply immediately thiab persist across kev sib ntsib. kev teeb tsa affect tag nrho cov ntawv throughout app suav nrog qhov chaw cov ntsiab, tau tsim cov khoom siv, thiab interface elements. Kev nkag mus tau kev teeb tsa here kev txhawb: low vision, dyslexia, kev pom stress, light sensitivity, thiab personal preference. Xa tawm kev teeb tsa mus sib koom nrog colleagues los yog coj los across devices.",
    "header_tools": "Kev nkag frequently-tau siv reading kev txhawb cov cuab yeej los ntawm header. muaj: Reading Ruler (horizontal kev tshawb bar), Focus Spotlight (dims surrounding thaj av), kab Focus (reading mask), cov ntawv-mus-Speech controls (suab, ceev, volume), Dictation (suab typing), thiab Timer (focus/Pomodoro). These cov cuab yeej work across tag nrho cov ntsiab views thiab tuaj yeem be combined (e.g., ruler + TTS + dark hom). cov cuab yeej yog designed rau chav kawm kev nkag mus tau needs without requiring app-wide kev teeb tsa kev hloov. txhua cov cuab yeej has ceev-hloov rau yooj yim qhib/kaw. Most cov cuab yeej suav nrog keyboard shortcuts—hover rau shortcut info.",
