    "header_actions": "cov ntsiab management actions. muaj: Khaws (disk lub cim, khaws current project), History (clock lub cim, kev nkag tau khaws kev sib ntsib), Sib koom (sib koom lub cim, xa tawm thiab distribution kev xaiv), thiab Luam tawm (printer lub cim, tsim printable version). Khaws tsim named snapshot hauv koj history. History qhib kev sib ntsib browser. Sib koom provides: link sharing, LMS xa tawm, colleague sharing, thiab tub ntxhais kawm distribution kev xaiv. tag nrho actions apply mus current project cov ntsiab. Actions auto-ua kom tiav hauv background qhov twg possible. Status indicators qhia khaws state thiab sync status. cov lus qhia: Khaws frequently thiab before switching activities mus preserve koj work.",
    "source_input": "Primary cov ntsiab kev nkag thaj av rau tag nrho tiam cov cuab yeej. Muab tso cov ntawv: Ctrl+V los yog sab xis-nyem muab tso. Type directly into field rau thawj cov ntsiab. Coj los kev xaiv: xa mus cov ntaub ntawv (PDF, DOCX, duab nrog OCR), coj los los ntawm URL, los yog AI-tsim cov ntsiab los ntawm cov ncauj lus. Qhov no becomes qhov chaw material rau tag nrho generators (phau ntawv qhia lus, kev sim, simplified cov ntawv, etc.). ntev guidance: 100-3000 lo lus ua hauj lwm best; longer cov ntsiab tuaj yeem be split. Rich formatting yog stripped—plain cov ntawv only. cov ntsiab yog analyzed by AI mus: rho tawm cov lus, txheeb xyuas ntsiab lus, thiab lub hom phiaj appropriate theem. Pro cov lus qhia: Suav nrog siab-quality qhov chaw cov ntsiab rau best tiam cov txiaj ntsig.",
    "source_settings_length": "Hais kom meej lo lus suav rau AI-tau tsim qhov chaw cov ntsiab. kev xaiv range los ntawm: 100 lo lus (luv overview), 250 lo lus (tus qauv nqe lus), 500 lo lus (luv article), mus 1000+ lo lus (comprehensive cov ntawv). Match ntev mus: intended reading time, tub ntxhais kawm attention span, thiab instructional purpose. Shorter cov ntawv work rau: ceev activities, younger tub ntxhais kawm, thiab focused xyaum. Longer cov ntawv work rau: comprehensive zaj lus qhia, older tub ntxhais kawm, thiab deep-dive cov ntsiab. Actual kev tawm may vary slightly los ntawm lub hom phiaj. AI maintains coherence regardless ntawm ntev. Consider qhov ntawd tau tsim cov ntsiab yuav be further processed by lwm cov cuab yeej—very ntev sources may overwhelm qee generators.",
    "source_settings_instructions": "Guide AI cov ntsiab tiam nrog tshwj xeeb cov lus qhia. piv txwv: Ua it engaging rau reluctant readers, Focus rau saum water cycle, Suav nrog diverse tus cwj pwm names, Avoid references mus violence, thiab Siv yooj yim cov lus rau ELL tub ntxhais kawm. cov lus qhia duab: suab, cov ntsiab focus, cov lus theem, thiab perspective. Be tshwj xeeb rau best cov txiaj ntsig. Multiple cov lus qhia tuaj yeem be combined. cov lus qhia yog processed along nrog koj cov ncauj lus thiab kev teeb tsa. Rau sensitive topics, suav nrog cov ntsiab guidance. cov lus qhia do tsis guarantee tshwj xeeb outcomes tab sis strongly influence tiam. cov lus qhia: Suav nrog theem qib kawm thiab any cov ntsiab restrictions hauv koj cov lus qhia rau most appropriate kev tawm.",
    "source_verify_checkbox": "Qhib AI fact-checking via Google Nrhiav grounding. thaum ON: AI cross-references tau tsim cov ntsiab against web sources, flagging los yog correcting potential inaccuracies. Adds 5-10 vib nas mus tiam time tab sis significantly improves reliability rau factual cov ntsiab. Especially important rau: history (dates, events), science (processes, cov ncauj lus), biography, thiab current events. Rau fiction, creative sau ntawv, los yog hypothetical scenarios, qhov no tuaj yeem be disabled mus allow ntau creative freedom. Sources consulted yog listed hauv tiam log rau xib fwb review. Highly recommended rau any cov ntsiab qhov ntawd yuav be presented as factual mus tub ntxhais kawm.",
    "source_generate_button": "Tsim AI-written cov ntsiab rau saum koj specified cov ncauj lus. Nyem mus begin tiam siv koj: cov ncauj lus description, lub hom phiaj ntev, theem qib kawm, thiab kev nyiam cov lus qhia. Tiam takes 10-20 vib nas. kev tawm yog reviewed by safety filters before tso tawm. Tsim tau cov ntsiab tuaj yeem be: edited (xib fwb tuaj yeem hloov any part), analyzed (khiav dhau los ntawm lwm tiam cov cuab yeej), thiab tau khaws (ntxiv mus history rau reuse). Siv thaum: koj need cov ntsiab rau saum tshwj xeeb cov ncauj lus, want controlled kev nyuaj, los yog need mus fill curriculum gaps. Tsim tau cov ntsiab muaj: appropriate cov lus, logical organization, thiab qib-theem syntax. Verify factual qhov tseeb before chav kawm siv.",
    "generator_actions": "Hub rau tag nrho cov ntsiab tiam cov cuab yeej. muaj generators suav nrog: kev sim (kev ntsuam xyuas nrog lo lus teb keys), phau ntawv qhia lus (kev pom cov lus), Simplified cov ntawv (leveled reading), FAQ (Q thiab pairs), Analysis (cov ntsiab examination), zaj lus qhia Kev npaj (instructional design), Timeline (chronological activity), Scaffolds (sau ntawv kev txhawb), Lub tswv yim Muab cais (categorization kev ua si), Lej (problem tiam), Adventure (interactive dab neeg), thiab Brainstorm (activity ideas). txhua generator transforms koj qhov chaw cov ntsiab into different hom. Nyem any generator mus qhib its configuration phab ntsa. Multiple generators tuaj yeem be tau siv rau saum tib yam qhov chaw. Tsim tau cov ntsiab tshwm hauv workspace thiab khaws mus history. cov lus qhia: Pib nrog Analysis mus nkag siab koj cov ntsiab, then tsim targeted kev pab cuam.",
    "tool_visual": "Kev nkag kev pom generator cov cuab yeej. Creates AI-tau tsim duab suav nrog: cov lus kev pom, lub tswv yim illustrations, qhov chaw depictions, duab piav qhia, thiab infographics. kev pom types: qhov xa mus duab (rau learning), worksheets (rau activities), thiab duab piav qhia (rau relationships). kev pom kev txhawb: ELL tub ntxhais kawm (kev pom cov lus), kev pom cov tub ntxhais kawm, thiab engagement. txhua tiam tsim unique duab. kev teeb tsa control hom, quality, thiab cov ntsiab. Tsim tau kev pom tuaj yeem be: downloaded, embedded hauv cov khoom siv, thiab added mus glossaries. Uses AI duab tiam credits. cov lus qhia: Tsim kev pom rau abstract lub tswv yim qhov ntawd yog difficult mus explain nrog lo lus alone.",
    "tool_udl": "Kawm txog UDL framework integration. Universal Design rau Learning has three principles: Multiple Means ntawm Representation ( dab tsi ntawm learning—present cov ncauj lus hauv different ways), Multiple Means ntawm Action thiab Expression ( yuav ua li cas ntawm learning—let tub ntxhais kawm demonstrate understanding differently), thiab Multiple Means ntawm Engagement ( why ntawm learning—motivate thiab sustain interest). Qhov no cov cuab yeej kev txhawb tag nrho three dhau los ntawm: varied cov ntsiab hom, multiple interaction hom, thiab gamified engagement. Clicking qhib meej cov ncauj lus txog yuav ua li cas txhua cov cuab yeej cov yam ntxwv aligns nrog UDL research. Zoo rau: professional development, IEP justification, thiab understanding pedagogical foundation. cov lus qhia: Qhov xa mus UDL principles thaum advocating rau cov cuab yeej adoption.",
