    "group_modal_container": "Organize tub ntxhais kawm into differentiated groups rau targeted cov lus qhia. Uses: assign different cov ntsiab mus different groups (leveled cov ntawv, varied kev sim), tsim collaborative teams, track performance by group, thiab manage ncaj qha kev sib ntsib nrog differentiated pushes. cov yam ntxwv: tsim/rename/lwv groups, rub-thiab-tso tub ntxhais kawm assignment, xim-code groups rau kev pom management, thiab assign tshwj xeeb kev pab cuam mus txhua group. kev txhawb: tiered cov lus qhia, station rotation, collaborative learning, thiab competition (team qhab nia). Connected tub ntxhais kawm pom only cov ntsiab assigned mus their group. Analytics sib piv group performance rau intervention decisions.",
    "group_create_input": "Name koj tshiab group rau organization. piv txwv: Red Team, qib siab Readers, lub rooj 3, los yog Period 2. Names should be memorable thiab appropriate rau tub ntxhais kawm saib yog tias shown. Keep names luv rau tso tawm purposes. Groups tuaj yeem be renamed later. Consider naming schemes: by ability (approaching, meeting, exceeding), by lub rooj/seating, by xim/ntsiab lus (teams), los yog by period (yog tias reusing kev sib ntsib). Group names tshwm sim hauv: tub ntxhais kawm saib (yog tias configured), analytics, thiab ncaj qha kev sib ntsib management. Avoid names qhov ntawd could embarrass tub ntxhais kawm los yog reveal ability theem publicly. Strategic naming helps koj quickly txheeb xyuas thiab manage tub ntxhais kawm groups during ncaj qha cov lus qhia.",
    "group_create_button": "Ntxiv named group mus koj kev sib ntsib. Nyem after entering group name. tshiab group tshwm hauv group phab ntsa ready rau tub ntxhais kawm assignment. Groups tuaj yeem be: assigned different cov ntsiab, tracked separately hauv analytics, thiab managed as units during ncaj qha kev sib ntsib. Tsis yog limit rau saum tus lej ntawm groups, tab sis 3-6 yog typical rau manageability. After creation: rub tub ntxhais kawm into group los yog siv bulk assignment. Groups persist across kev sib ntsib yog tias siv cloud sync. Empty groups tuaj yeem be deleted. txhua group tuaj yeem muaj different kev pab cuam assigned. cov lus qhia: Tsim groups before tub ntxhais kawm join so they tuaj yeem be assigned immediately rau saum connection.",
    "group_resource_library": "Collection ntawm tag nrho tau tsim cov khoom siv muaj rau assignment. Shows: kev sim, glossaries, adventures, activities, thiab tag nrho tau tsim cov ntsiab los ntawm qhov no kev sib ntsib. Rub kev pab cuam mus reorder rau presentation sequence. kev pab cuam tuaj yeem be: assigned mus tag nrho tub ntxhais kawm (default), assigned mus tshwj xeeb groups only, los yog hidden los ntawm tub ntxhais kawm. txhua kev pab cuam qhia: type lub cim, title/description, thiab assignment status. Lim by type yog tias library yog large. kev pab cuam assigned mus groups qhia colored indicator matching group xim. tshiab generations automatically tshwm sim here. cov lus qhia: Prepare tag nrho kev pab cuam before ncaj qha kev sib ntsib, then assign strategically during cov lus qhia.",
    "group_active_list": "phab ntsa qhia tag nrho tau tsim groups nrog assignment kev xaiv. txhua group displays: name, tub ntxhais kawm suav, assigned kev pab cuam, thiab ceev actions. Rub kev pab cuam los ntawm library mus groups rau differentiated assignment. Multiple kev pab cuam tuaj yeem be assigned per group. Nyem group name mus expand thiab pom: tus kheej tub ntxhais kawm, meej assignments, thiab group-tshwj xeeb kev teeb tsa. Groups tuaj yeem muaj different: cov ntsiab theem, hom lus, thiab activity types. Siv rau tiered cov lus qhia: lower group gets scaffolded cov ntsiab, higher group gets extensions. Ncaj qha kev sib ntsib pushes respect group assignments. Analytics separate by group rau yooj yim comparison. xim-coded rau ceev kev pom identification.",
    "group_roster_list": "Daim ntawv teev npe ntawm tag nrho tub ntxhais kawm currently connected mus koj kev sib ntsib. Rub tub ntxhais kawm mus different groups los yog siv dropdown mus assign. default: tag nrho tub ntxhais kawm join General group. Pom at glance: tub ntxhais kawm name/codename, connection status (green = qhib, yellow = idle, gray = disconnected), current group assignment, thiab kawg activity timestamp. Nyem tub ntxhais kawm name mus saib their tus kheej kev nce qib. Multi-xaiv: hold Shift thiab nyem mus xaiv multiple tub ntxhais kawm rau bulk group assignment. cov lus qhia: Tsim groups before tub ntxhais kawm join, los yog assign hauv real-time as koj assess readiness theem during kev sib ntsib.",
    "header_language": "Teeb tso tawm hom lus rau tag nrho UI elements (pob nias, labels, menu). muaj hom lus yog pre-translated rau immediate siv. Rau lwm hom lus, siv Translate cov yam ntxwv mus tsim tshiab kev txhais lus. Interface hom lus yog separate los ntawm cov ntsiab hom lus—koj tuaj yeem muaj Spanish interface while tab tom tsim English cov ntsiab. Perfect rau: ELL tub ntxhais kawm, ob hom lus classrooms, heritage hom lus kev txhawb, thiab niam txiv kev nkag mus tau. hom lus preference yog tau khaws per user. Qee specialized lo lus remain hauv English thaum no equivalent exists. Pro cov lus qhia: niam txiv tuaj yeem teeb their preferred hom lus mus participate hauv their child educational cov ntsiab.",
