    "header_export": "Xa tawm koj tau tsim cov ntsiab hauv multiple hom rau different siv. PDF: Luam tawm-ready cov ntawv nrog formatting preserved—zoo rau handouts, worksheets, thiab physical cov khoom siv. Slides: PowerPoint/Google Slides hom rau chav kawm presentation. Canvas/LMS kev sim (QTI): Industry-tus qauv hom compatible nrog Canvas, Blackboard, Moodle, thiab lwm LMS platforms—imports nrog lo lus teb keys intact. HTML: Tus kheej-contained web phab ntawv rau posting mus chav kawm websites los yog sharing via links. IMS Feem ntau Cartridge: Ua kom tiav zaj lus qhia package rau LMS coj los. tag nrho exports suav nrog kev nkag mus tau cov yam ntxwv thiab tuaj yeem be customized before rub los.",
