    "chat_input": "koj communication channel nrog AlloBot, AI teaching assistant. Ask txog: yuav ua li cas mus siv tshwj xeeb cov yam ntxwv (qhov twg yog phau ntawv qhia lus?), pedagogical guidance (yuav ua li cas should I differentiate qhov no cov ntawv?), cov ntsiab explanations (Explain photosynthesis simply), thiab workflow kev pab (dab tsi should I tsim thawj?). AlloBot yog context-aware: it knows dab tsi cov ntsiab koj muaj loaded thiab tuaj yeem ua tshwj xeeb suggestions. suab hom muaj: nyem microphone mus hais instead ntawm type. kev sib tham history yog tau khaws rau koj kev sib ntsib. Pro cov lus qhia: After pasting cov ntsiab, ask dab tsi learning activities would work well nrog qhov no? rau tailored recommendations.",
