    "chat_grade_select": "Teeb theem qib kawm lim rau tus qauv thiab cov ntsiab. Selection affects: which tus qauv yog shown, reading theem recommendations, thiab age-appropriate suggestions. qib bands muaj: Pre-K, K-2, 3-5, 6-8, 9-12, thiab Higher Ed. tus qauv consultation filters mus tau xaiv qib. cov ntsiab recommendations align nrog qib expectations. tuaj yeem be changed per query—tsis locked globally. Multi-qib classrooms tuaj yeem kho per activity. theem qib kawm also influences: cov lus kev nyuaj, kab lus structure, thiab lub tswv yim scaffolding hauv AI suggestions. cov lus qhia: Teeb accurately mus get most relevant tus qauv thiab suggestions rau koj tub ntxhais kawm.",
