    "chat_autofill": "ua nws tus kheej configuration assistance los ntawm AI analysis. thaum enabled: AlloBot reads koj qhov chaw cov ntsiab, extracts key cov ncauj lus (cov ncauj lus, cov lus, ntsiab lus, approximate theem qib kawm), thiab pre-fills cov cuab yeej kev teeb tsa. Benefits: faster setup, consistent kev sib raug, thiab reduced siv tes configuration. Pre-filled kev teeb tsa tuaj yeem be adjusted before tiam. Autofill examines: cov lus kev nyuaj, subject matter, cov ntawv structure, thiab cov ntsiab ntsiab lus. Ua hauj lwm best nrog: well-structured qhov chaw cov ntawv, clear educational cov ntsiab, thiab sufficient cov ntsiab ntev. Kaw only yog tias: koj prefer full siv tes control los yog autofill suggestions yog consistently wrong. cov lus qhia: Leave enabled rau efficiency—koj tuaj yeem always override tus kheej kev teeb tsa.",
    "analysis_generate_button": "Khiav AI analysis rau saum koj qhov chaw cov ntsiab. Tiam time depends rau saum tob kev teeb tsa. kev tawm muaj: readability statistics, main idea cov ntsiab lus, key cov lus nrog lub ntsiab, ntsiab lus identification, cov ntawv structure analysis, potential tub ntxhais kawm misconceptions, discussion lo lus nug, thiab teaching opportunity highlights. cov txiaj ntsig tshwm sim hauv organized tsab ntawv ceeb toom hom. Analysis informs: which cov cuab yeej mus tsim tom ntej, yuav ua li cas mus differentiate, thiab dab tsi mus pre-teach. Xa tawm analysis rau zaj lus qhia planning documentation. Analysis reveals dab tsi might be challenging rau tub ntxhais kawm before they encounter it. Siv insights mus anticipate lo lus nug thiab prepare kev txhawb.",
    "outline_generate_button": "Tsim organized representation ntawm koj cov ntsiab. kev tawm kev xaiv suav nrog: Traditional Outline (hierarchical nrog Roman numerals), Lub tswv yim Map (kev pom connections nyob nruab nrab ideas), Bullet Cov ntsiab lus (streamlined key lub tshoj), thiab Cornell Notes Template (pre-structured nrog cue kem). hom selection tshwm before tiam. AI identifies: main ideas, supporting kev meej, relationships, thiab key cov lus. Outlines tuaj yeem be: filled hauv by AI (ua kom tiav) los yog left as templates (tub ntxhais kawm ua kom tiav). Interactive version allow expanding/collapsing tshooj. Xa tawm rau handouts los yog digital distribution. Zoo rau: pre-reading overview, study guides, thiab note-taking scaffolds.",
    "dashboard_import_btn": "Nqa los tub ntxhais kawm records los ntawm spreadsheet cov ntaub ntawv. CSV hom must suav nrog: tub ntxhais kawm identifier (name los yog codename hauv kem ). tsis yog yuav tsum kem: group assignment, preset accommodations, prior qhab nia, thiab kev nyiam fields. Template muaj rau rub los qhia expected hom. Coj los merges nrog existing cov ncauj lus los yog replaces based rau saum koj selection. Siv rau: starting tshiab semester nrog rosters, syncing los ntawm SIS xa tawm, los yog restoring los ntawm backup. Imported tub ntxhais kawm tshwm sim hauv roster ready rau group assignment. Large imports may take moment. Validate coj los cov txiaj ntsig before relying rau saum cov ncauj lus. cov lus qhia: Xa tawm koj roster thawj mus pom expected hom.",
