    "settings_perm_visuals": "Control tub ntxhais kawm kev nkag mus duab tiam. thaum enabled: tub ntxhais kawm tuaj yeem request AI-tau tsim kev pom, supporting kev pom cov tub ntxhais kawm thiab engagement. thaum disabled: duab tiam yog xib fwb-only, reducing API costs thiab keeping focus rau saum cov ntawv. Qhib rau: creative projects, kev pom kev txhawb needs, thiab exploratory learning. Kaw rau: cov ntawv-focused zaj lus qhia, budget conservation, thiab reducing distraction. txhua duab tiam siv API credits. tub ntxhais kawm-tau tsim duab yog cov ntsiab-filtered tab sis may vary hauv quality. Analytics track tiam frequency. duab khaws mus gallery rau reuse. cov lus qhia: Qhib rau projects qhov twg visualization helps; kaw thaum cov ntawv kev nkag siab yog primary lub hom phiaj.",
