    "history_load_project": "Reload ua kom tiav project los ntawm koj tau khaws history. Restoring muaj: tag nrho qhov chaw cov ntsiab, every tau tsim kev pab cuam (phau ntawv qhia lus, kev sim, zaj lus qhia kev npaj, etc.), tub ntxhais kawm kev nce qib cov ncauj lus thiab XP, kev teeb tsa thiab preferences, thiab kev sib ntsib notes. Loading replaces current workspace—khaws current work thawj yog tias needed. Siv rau: continuing multi-day projects, reusing proven zaj lus qhia cov khoom siv, thiab reviewing past work. Projects yog named by date thiab cov ntsiab, los yog kev nyiam label yog tias koj provided one. Deleted projects cannot be recovered, so archive important ones. Cloud sync ensures projects yog pom tau los ntawm any device.",
