    "ws_gen_minimize": "Collapse lo lus Word Sounds Studio phab ntsa mus compact bar. background becomes pom tau while studio remains pom tau. Siv thaum: koj need mus qhov xa mus lwm cov ntsiab, want tsawg kev pom clutter, los yog checking something behind phab ntsa. Studio state yog preserved—tag nrho kev teeb tsa thiab kev nce qib remain intact. Nyem bar los yog expand pob nias mus restore full phab ntsa. Minimizing does tsis pause activities los yog affect kev nce qib. Studio tuaj yeem be repositioned thaum minimized. cov lus qhia: Minimize mus check tub ntxhais kawm kev pab cuam los yog qhov xa mus cov khoom siv without closing phonics activity.",
