    "ws_gen_expand": "Restore lo lus Word Sounds Studio mus full phab ntsa saib. Expands los ntawm minimized state mus qhia tag nrho controls thiab kev xaiv. tag nrho kev teeb tsa thiab kev nce qib yog preserved during minimize/expand cycles. Siv mus: kev nkag full configuration, pom ua kom tiav lo lus daim ntawv teev npe, los yog interact nrog tag nrho studio cov yam ntxwv. Expand yog inverse ntawm minimize. phab ntsa qhib mus koj kawg qhov chaw thiab size. cov lus qhia: Expand thaum ready mus configure los yog review, minimize during qhib tub ntxhais kawm xyaum.",
    "ws_gen_ortho_slider": "Controls yuav ua li cas many spelling (orthography) activities yog suav nrog per kev sib ntsib. Slide sab xis mus ntxiv spelling xyaum after phonics activities ua kom tiav. thaum teeb mus 0 (Off), no spelling activities yog tau tsim. thaum controlled by zaj lus qhia Kev npaj hom, qhov no slider yog locked thiab managed automatically. Spelling activities reinforce sound-mus-letter mapping tub ntxhais kawm kawm during phonics, strengthening encoding kev txawj alongside decoding.",
    "ws_gen_review_btn": "Qhib cov ntsiab lus saib ntawm tag nrho lo lus hauv current phonics zaj lus qhia. Review phab ntsa qhia: ua kom tiav lo lus daim ntawv teev npe, phonetic transcriptions, syllable counts, thiab qhov chaw indicators (phau ntawv qhia lus, lo lus family, kev nyiam). Siv mus: verify lo lus selection before starting, check zaj lus qhia coverage, thiab txheeb xyuas any lo lus mus hloov. lo lus tuaj yeem be: removed (nyem X), reordered (rub), los yog regenerated (nyem tshiab dua rau saum tus kheej yam). Review before starting helps ensure zaj lus qhia targets intended kev txawj. Luam tawm kev xaiv tsim lo lus daim ntawv teev npe handout. cov lus qhia: Review thiab kho lo lus daim ntawv teev npe before tub ntxhais kawm kev sib ntsib rau optimal zaj lus qhia kev sib raug.",
    "ws_gen_count_slider": "Teeb total tus lej ntawm lo lus hauv koj phonics zaj lus qhia. Range: 5 lo lus (ceev xyaum, ~5 minutes) mus 30 lo lus (comprehensive kev sib ntsib, ~25 minutes). Consider: attention span (younger = fewer lo lus), kev txawj theem (sib tw readers need ntau repetition ntawm fewer lo lus), kev sib ntsib type (intervention vs. enrichment). txhua lo lus muaj: suab pronunciation, phoneme breakdown, AI-tau tsim duab, thiab interactive activities. ntau lo lus = ntau variety tab sis longer kev sib ntsib. Fewer lo lus = deeper xyaum nrog txhua. Rau RTI Tier 2/3 intervention, 8-12 lo lus nrog multiple repetitions yog typically recommended. Kho based rau saum tub ntxhais kawm response.",
    "ws_gen_session_slider": "Define mastery threshold rau kev sib ntsib kev ua tiav. Range: 3 correct (ceev check) mus 20 correct (extended xyaum). txhua correct lo lus teb: advances kev nce qib bar, awards XP, thiab reinforces learning. Incorrect lo lus teb: provide feedback tab sis do tsis subtract los ntawm lub hom phiaj. kev sib ntsib ends thaum threshold yog met, rewarding persistence. Higher thresholds = ntau xyaum = stronger retention. Lower thresholds = quicker kev ua tiav = ntau kev sib ntsib possible. Rau sib tw readers, pib nrog achievable lub hom phiaj (5-8) mus tsim confidence. Rau fluent readers, higher lub hom phiaj maintain engagement. kev nce qib auto-khaws so tub ntxhais kawm tuaj yeem mus ntxiv later yog tias needed.",
    "ws_gen_theme_input": "Hloov raws siab nyiam kev pom hom rau cov lus duab. Sau hom descriptions like: pixel art (retro kev ua si look), watercolor (soft painterly), cartoon (bright kid-friendly), realistic photo (accurate qhov xa mus), los yog sketch (yooj yim kab drawings). hom applies mus tag nrho tau tsim lo lus duab. Leave blank rau default hom. hom affects engagement thiab appropriateness rau age. Qee hom work zoo dua rau certain cov ntsiab. kev sim mus find dab tsi resonates nrog koj tub ntxhais kawm. cov lus qhia: Siv cartoon los yog pixel art rau younger tub ntxhais kawm, realistic rau older grades studying science cov lus.",
    "ws_gen_syllable_min": "Teeb minimum syllable suav rau tau tsim lo lus. Range: 1 syllable (cat, dog) mus 4+ syllables (hippopotamus). Syllable suav correlates nrog decoding kev nyuaj. 1-syllable lo lus: CVC cov qauv, beginning readers, phoneme segmentation focus. 2-syllable lo lus: introduce syllable kev faib, compound lo lus, affixes. 3+ syllable lo lus: qib siab decoding, morphology awareness. Siv nrog Max Syllables mus tsim tshwj xeeb ranges: teeb ob qho mus 2 rau two-syllable xyaum only. cov lus qhia: kev nce qib los ntawm fewer syllables mus ntau as tub ntxhais kawm tsim kev txawj. Multisyllabic lo lus cov lus qhia yog critical rau upper elementary fluency development.",
    "ws_gen_syllable_max": "Teeb upper limit rau lo lus syllable suav. Ua hauj lwm nrog Minimum slider mus tsim ranges. piv txwv: Min 1, Max 2 tsim one thiab two syllable lo lus. Min 2, Max 4 tsim multisyllabic kev sib tw lo lus. Teeb ob qho sib npaug rau tshwj xeeb syllable xyaum. Higher maximums suav nrog: longer lo lus, ntau nyuaj decoding, thiab qib siab cov lus. Consider theem qib kawm: K-1 typically 1-2 syllables, 2-3 up mus 3 syllables, 4+ tuaj yeem handle 4+ syllables. Syllable suav affects activity duration. cov lus qhia: Gradually increase maximum as tub ntxhais kawm master current range.",
