    "ws_gen_src_family": "Focus xyaum rau saum rhyming lo lus cov qauv. lo lus families (rimes) sib koom: ending cov suab, spelling cov qauv, thiab decoding tswv yim. piv txwv: -at family (cat, hat, bat), -ight family (light, night, sab xis). Learning lo lus families: tsim pattern recognition, accelerates decoding ntawm tshiab lo lus, thiab develops phonemic awareness. Xaiv family los ntawm dropdown after enabling qhov no kev xaiv. AI expands family nrog additional valid lo lus. Perfect rau: beginning readers, pattern-based cov lus qhia, thiab rhyme awareness. cov lus qhia: Teach one lo lus family thoroughly before introducing another.",
