    "ws_gen_src_custom": "Tsim kev nyiam lo lus daim ntawv teev npe rau targeted xyaum. Qhib qhov no kev xaiv mus ntxiv koj own lo lus. Siv rau: curriculum-tshwj xeeb cov lus, commonly misspelled lo lus, tub ntxhais kawm-requested lo lus, thiab intervention targets. Custom lo lus txais full phonetic processing: IPA, syllables, duab, thiab activities. Tsis yog limit rau saum kev nyiam lo lus. Mix nrog lwm lo lus sources los yog siv kev nyiam-only. lo lus yog validated rau phonetic compatibility. Zoo rau: differentiation, IEP lub hom phiaj, thiab personalized xyaum. cov lus qhia: Ntxiv lo lus tub ntxhais kawm struggle nrog hauv reading rau targeted phonics kev txhawb.",
