    "adventure_setup_input_mode": "Xaiv primary gameplay mechanic. Kev xaiv: pick los ntawm AI-tau tsim kev xaiv txhua turn (easiest, dab neeg-focused). Debate: persuade NPCs dhau los ntawm argument (tsim rhetoric, critical thinking). system Simulation: manage kev pab cuam like kub, health, reputation (teaches consequences, economics). txhua hom fundamentally kev hloov gameplay experience. Choice hom yog best rau: younger tub ntxhais kawm, zaj dab neeg focus, structured zaj lus qhia. Debate hom develops: argumentation, pov thawj siv, perspective-taking. system hom teaches: kev pab cuam management, cause-effect, planning. cov lus qhia: Pib nrog Kev xaiv mus kawm interface, graduate mus lwm hom rau kev txawj development.",
    "adventure_setup_difficulty": "Teeb overall adventure kev sib tw. dab neeg (yooj yim): forgiving outcomes, zaj dab neeg focus, no fail states. Normal: balanced kev sib tw, meaningful consequences. Challenging: higher stakes, kev pab cuam scarcity. Hardcore: strict penalties, possible kev poob. kev nyuaj affects: yuav ua li cas forgiving kev xaiv yog, kev pab cuam availability, consequence severity, thiab stakes ntawm decisions. Lower kev nyuaj yog best rau: engagement focus, younger tub ntxhais kawm, sensitive cov tub ntxhais kawm. Higher kev nyuaj ua hauj lwm rau: older tub ntxhais kawm, tswv yim xyaum, learning los ntawm consequences. kev nyuaj tuaj yeem be adjusted mid-adventure. cov lus qhia: Pib easier thiab increase as tub ntxhais kawm become comfortable nrog hom.",
    "adventure_setup_language": "Xaiv narration thiab dialogue hom lus. kev xaiv suav nrog: English (default), Spanish, French, German, Mandarin, thiab 30+ others. tag nrho AI cov ntawv siv tau xaiv hom lus. cov lus yog qib-appropriate within chosen hom lus. ob hom lus hom qhia ob qho hom lus side-by-side. hom lus immersion kev txhawb: world hom lus chav kawm, heritage hom lus xyaum, thiab ELL cov ntsiab-based cov lus qhia. Switching hom lus mid-adventure yog possible. dab neeg cov ntsiab adapts culturally thaum appropriate. tus cwj pwm names thiab kev teeb tsa may kho mus match linguistic context. cov lus qhia: Siv rau authentic hom lus xyaum hauv engaging zaj dab neeg context.",
    "adventure_setup_chk_freeresponse": "Qhib qhib-ended response kev nkag. thaum ON: tub ntxhais kawm type any action they want, AI adapts dab neeg accordingly, creative freedom yog maximized. thaum OFF: tub ntxhais kawm xaiv los ntawm 4 AI-tau tsim kev xaiv, structure guides experience. Free response tsim: composition kev txawj, creativity, agency. kev xaiv hom provides: scaffolding, guaranteed productive kev xaiv, kev nkag mus tau. Free response may lead mus unexpected dab neeg directions. AI handles most reasonable kev nkag. cov lus qhia: Pib nrog kev xaiv OFF mus teach dab neeg context, qhib later rau tub ntxhais kawm-driven exploration.",
    "adventure_setup_chk_chance": "Ntxiv tabletop RPG-hom randomness. thaum enabled: risky actions trigger D20 roll, roll cov txiaj ntsig affects kev kov yeej los yog kev poob, critical successes (20) thiab failures (1) tsim memorable moments. Teaches: probability lub tswv yim, risk vs. nqi zog, accepting uncertain outcomes. Roll animation qhia rau saum screen. tub ntxhais kawm kawm mus weigh odds before attempting risky actions. Chance hom adds: excitement, unpredictability, thiab consequence learning. Without chance: outcomes yog deterministic based rau saum kev xaiv. cov lus qhia: Qhib rau older tub ntxhais kawm who enjoy tswv yim kev ua si thiab tuaj yeem handle random kev poob.",
    "adventure_setup_chk_story": "Simplify interface rau pure storytelling. thaum ON: kev pab cuam phab ntsa yog hidden, no stats mus track, zaj dab neeg-only experience. thaum OFF: full system visibility, kev pab cuam displayed, kev ua si-like interface. dab neeg hom yog best rau: younger tub ntxhais kawm, reading focus, reduced cognitive nqa los. Full hom engages: gamers, tswv yim lovers, older tub ntxhais kawm. dab neeg hom still tracks internal kev nce qib tab sis does tsis tso tawm it. Switching during adventure reveals los yog hides phab ntsa. cov lus qhia: Siv dab neeg hom rau thawj experience, ntxiv stats later rau tub ntxhais kawm who want kev ua si elements.",
