    "adventure_start_btn": "Pib adventure nrog configured kev teeb tsa. Starting: tsim opening qhov chaw, tsim initial kev xaiv, thiab begins zaj dab neeg. Uses tag nrho kev teeb tsa configured hauv setup phab ntsa. Starting tshiab replaces any hauv-kev nce qib adventure (khaws thawj via Resume yog tias needed). thawj qhov chaw takes 10-15 vib nas mus tsim as AI tsim initial dab neeg state. Adventure auto-khaws after txhua qhov chaw. Multiple adventures tuaj yeem be tau khaws separately. cov lus qhia: Verify kev teeb tsa before starting since qee cannot be changed mid-adventure.",
    "adventure_resume_btn": "Return mus koj hauv-kev nce qib adventure. Resume loads: koj exact dab neeg qhov chaw, tag nrho kev xaiv made, inventory thiab kev pab cuam, thiab zaj dab neeg context. Perfect rau: multi-kev sib ntsib adventures, continuing after breaks, thiab picking up qhov twg koj left off. Resume yog only muaj thaum tau khaws kev nce qib exists. Resume pob nias qhia: adventure title thiab kawg played timestamp. Multiple adventures tuaj yeem be tau khaws; xaiv which mus resume. Unsaved kev nce qib since kawg auto-khaws may be lost. cov lus qhia: Adventures auto-khaws after txhua decision, tab sis manually khaws before closing rau safety.",
    "adventure_immersive_toggle_ui": "Hloov UI visibility during adventure. thaum hidden: maximum dab neeg immersion, fullscreen zaj dab neeg, minimal distraction. thaum shown: kev nkag mus tag nrho controls, kev teeb tsa, thiab inventory. Hloov anytime during ua si. Hidden hom yog zoo rau: reading focus, presentations, thiab cinematic experience. pom tau hom needed rau: kev teeb tsa kev nkag, inventory management, thiab xib fwb controls. dab neeg continues normally hauv ob qho hom. Keyboard shortcut muaj. Touch edges mus reveal UI thaum hidden. cov lus qhia: Zais UI thaum tub ntxhais kawm yog reading, qhia thaum making kev xaiv los yog checking inventory.",
    "adventure_immersive_exit": "Leave fullscreen immersive experience. Clicking exits mus: tus qauv adventure saib, pom tau controls, thiab normal interface. Adventure continues los ntawm current qhov chaw. kev nce qib yog preserved. Siv thaum: needing mus kev nkag kev teeb tsa, switching activities, los yog finished playing. Immersive hom tuaj yeem be re-entered anytime. Exit does tsis end adventure. Keyboard shortcut: Escape key also exits. cov lus qhia: Exit immersive hom thaum koj need mus kev pab tub ntxhais kawm los yog kev nkag xib fwb controls.",
