    "adventure_immersive_inventory": "Kev nkag collected yam while hauv immersive saib. Inventory qhia: tag nrho yam acquired during adventure, yam descriptions thiab siv, thiab current kev pab cuam counts. yam may be: usable (consumables), key yam (dab neeg-important), los yog equipment (stat-affecting). Nyem yam mus siv los yog inspect. Inventory management yog part ntawm gameplay hauv system Simulation hom. Qee yam yog yuav tsum tau mus kev nce qib. cov lus qhia: Check inventory regularly mus remember dab tsi kev pab cuam koj muaj muaj rau solving kev sib tw.",
    "adventure_choice_toggle": "Expand mus qhia muaj kev xaiv. Nyem mus reveal 4 AI-tau tsim kev xaiv rau current dab neeg beat. Kev xaiv yog: contextually appropriate, varied hauv approach, thiab balanced hauv outcome potential. Zais again by clicking. Choice visibility tuaj yeem be controlled by xib fwb. tub ntxhais kawm tuaj yeem request different kev xaiv. txhua choice leads mus unique dab neeg continuation. Kev xaiv suav nrog: dialogue kev xaiv, actions, thiab decisions. cov lus qhia: Nyeem tag nrho kev xaiv before selecting mus find one qhov ntawd best matches koj intent.",
    "adventure_choice_btn": "Lees paub qhov no choice mus advance zaj dab neeg. Clicking: submits koj decision, tsim dab neeg continuation, thiab presents tshiab qhov chaw thiab kev xaiv. Decision yog logged rau xib fwb review. XP may be awarded based rau saum choice quality. dab neeg adapts mus koj decision. Qee kev xaiv muaj immediate consequences; others affect later dab neeg. Kev xaiv cannot be undone without xib fwb intervention. AI remembers tag nrho dhau los kev xaiv rau zaj dab neeg consistency. cov lus qhia: Consider consequences before choosing, especially hauv challenging kev nyuaj hom.",
    "adventure_input_field": "Free-cov ntawv kev nkag rau kev nyiam actions. muaj thaum Free Response yog enabled. Type any action koj want koj tus cwj pwm mus take. AI interprets: movement, dialogue, investigation, thiab creative actions. Clear, tshwj xeeb actions work best. Vague kev nkag may lead mus unexpected interpretations. Grammar thiab spelling affect AI understanding. tus cwj pwm limits exist rau practical reasons. kev nkag yog processed by cov ntsiab filters rau safety. cov lus qhia: Sau ua kom tiav kab lus describing koj action rau best cov txiaj ntsig.",
    "adventure_input_send": "Lees paub thiab xa koj typed action. Nyem after typing koj desired action. AI processes kev nkag thiab tsim dab neeg response. Processing takes 5-10 vib nas. Submission yog logged rau review. Cannot be undone after sending. AI handles most reasonable actions. Nonsensical kev nkag may tsim unexpected cov txiaj ntsig. Clear, appropriate actions yield best dab neeg continuation. cov lus qhia: Re-nyeem koj action before submitting mus ensure it says dab tsi koj mean.",
    "adventure_edit_options": "xib fwb-only cov yam ntxwv mus hloov AI-tau tsim kev xaiv. Kev nkag mus: kho choice cov ntawv, ntxiv kev nyiam kev xaiv, tshem inappropriate kev xaiv, thiab reorder rau emphasis. Siv thaum: AI tau tsim unsuitable kev xaiv, koj want mus guide tshwj xeeb learning, los yog need curriculum kev sib raug. Edits only pom tau hauv xib fwb saib until applied. tub ntxhais kawm pom finalized kev xaiv. Kev hloov take effect rau current qhov chaw. AI adapts future generations based rau saum cov qauv. cov lus qhia: Kho kev xaiv mus zoo dua align nrog learning objectives los yog tshem distracting kev xaiv.",
    "democracy_toggle": "Collaborative decision-making hom. thaum ON: tag nrho connected tub ntxhais kawm vote rau saum tom ntej action, majority choice advances dab neeg, real-time vote tso tawm qhia consensus. Creates: shared adventure experience, discussion opportunities, thiab democratic xyaum. Voting period yog configurable. Ties tuaj yeem be settled randomly los yog by xib fwb. tub ntxhais kawm pom their classmates votes. Promotes: collaboration, deliberation, thiab community. Best rau: whole-chav kawm adventures, discussion-based zaj lus qhia, thiab SEL integration. cov lus qhia: Siv chav kawm voting rau shared adventures projected rau saum screen.",
    "crossword_close_btn": "Exit crossword activity. Closing khaws: current kev nce qib, filled letters, thiab kev ua tiav status. Resume los ntawm Crossword cov cuab yeej mus mus ntxiv. Partially completed puzzles remain muaj. XP yog awarded rau saum full kev ua tiav only. Kaw thaum: switching activities, needing break, los yog finished playing. kev nce qib auto-khaws every few vib nas. Reopening qhia koj tau khaws state. cov lus qhia: Ua kom tiav at least few lo lus before closing mus capture kev nce qib.",
