    "adventure_art_style": "Art hom Selection: Xaiv kev pom art hom rau AI-tau tsim adventure illustrations. kev xaiv suav nrog Auto (lets AI pick), phau ntawv dab neeg (classic children's illustration), Watercolor, Anime, Pixel Art, thiab ntau. Different hom tsim different atmospheres rau dab neeg — phau ntawv dab neeg ua hauj lwm well rau younger readers, while Anime los yog Pixel Art may engage older tub ntxhais kawm. hom applies mus tag nrho qhov chaw illustrations hauv adventure.",
