    "quiz_csv_export_btn": "Rub los gradebook as wide-hom CSV: one kab per tub ntxhais kawm nrog cov ntsiab lus kem (Answered, Correct, IDK, qhab nia %) followed by 4 kem per lo lus nug (Status, lo lus teb, Confidence, AI Feedback). Opens hauv Excel, Google Sheets, tus lej, thiab most tsev kawm ntawv gradebook system (PowerSchool, Aspen, Infinite Campus, Google chav kawm).",
    "quiz_teacher_override_row": "Override AI's qib rau qhib-response yam. Nyem ✓ rau correct, ✗ rau incorrect, ◐ rau partially correct. xib fwb override beats AI cache thiab deterministic grader, so koj judgment yog final. Nyem tib yam pob nias again (los yog ↺ undo) mus tshem override thiab revert mus AI qib. Persists hauv ncaj qha kev sib ntsib thiab recomputes gradebook qhab nia immediately.",
    "quiz_distractor_review_summary": "After Pre-Check los yog Formative Check tiam, kev ntsuam xyuas-design AI evaluates whether txhua distractor encodes real tub ntxhais kawm misconception (vs. random plausibly-wrong lo lus teb). Qhov no cov ntsiab lus qhia: yuav ua li cas many distractors encode misconceptions, overall quality feem pua, thiab which lo lus nug mus review before deploying. Hauv kho hom, 'Improve tag nrho N' pob nias rewrites every flagged distractor hauv one batch.",
    "quiz_image_refine_btn": "Refine qhov no duab hauv place without regenerating whole kev sim. Nyem pencil pob nias rau saum any kev sim duab (only pom tau hauv kho hom) mus qhib inline phab ntsa: type kev nyiam cov lus qhia (e.g., 'ua background pure white', 'ntxiv clearer label') thiab submit, OR nyem '🧹 Tshem cov ntawv' ceev-action rau one-nyem cov ntawv removal. hom cov lus qhia teeb at tiam time yog preserved across refines.",
