    "persona_generate_button": "Tsim AI personas automatically los ntawm koj qhov chaw cov ntsiab. system analyzes koj cov ntawv mus txheeb xyuas key figures, historical periods, los yog tus cwj pwm archetypes thiab tsim authentic conversational partners. Tsim tau personas suav nrog accurate biographical kev meej, period-appropriate cov lus, thiab contextual knowledge limitations (they won't know txog events after their time).",
    "persona_select_button": "Xaiv qhov no persona mus begin koj interview los yog conversation. Once tau xaiv, koj'll sau immersive kev sib tham interface qhov twg koj tuaj yeem ask lo lus nug, nrhiav xyuas their perspective, thiab earn XP rau meaningful exchanges. AI responds based rau saum tus cwj pwm's historical knowledge, personality, thiab cultural context.",
    "persona_back_btn": "Return mus persona selection screen mus xaiv different tus cwj pwm. koj current conversation kev nce qib yog automatically tau khaws, thiab koj tuaj yeem return mus mus ntxiv it later. Qhov no allows exploring multiple perspectives rau saum tib yam historical cov ncauj lus.",
    "persona_custom_instructions": "Ntxiv tshwj xeeb requirements rau yuav ua li cas persona should behave during conversations. piv txwv: focus rau saum tshwj xeeb time period, emphasize certain beliefs los yog tus nqi, maintain particular speech cov qauv, los yog limit responses mus historically accurate knowledge. xib fwb tuaj yeem siv qhov no mus align personas nrog tshwj xeeb learning objectives.",
    "persona_response_mode": "Xaiv yuav ua li cas persona responds mus tsim different learning experiences. IN tus cwj pwm: Fully immersive historical suab nrog no modern explanations. EDUCATIONAL: tus cwj pwm speaks tab sis muaj learning scaffolds, cov lus kev txhawb, thiab context. MIXED: Balanced approach nrog authentic suab plus occasional clarifications. Xaiv based rau saum tub ntxhais kawm readiness thiab learning lub hom phiaj.",
    "persona_free_response": "Type koj own qhib-ended response instead ntawm selecting los ntawm pre-written kev xaiv. Free response hom promotes creative expression, critical thinking, thiab authentic dialogue kev txawj. Responses yog analyzed rau historical qhov tseeb, empathy, thiab tob ntawm inquiry. Higher-quality lo lus nug earn ntau XP.",
    "persona_hints_toggle": "Qhia los yog zais response suggestions thiab conversation cov lus qhia. thaum enabled, system provides scaffolded lo lus nug starters, historical context cov lus qhia, thiab engagement suggestions. Helpful rau tub ntxhais kawm tshiab mus historical inquiry los yog those needing kev txhawb nrog qhib-ended questioning. xib fwb tuaj yeem kaw cov lus qhia rau ntau qib siab kev ntsuam xyuas scenarios.",
    "persona_show_hints": "Tso tawm helpful cov lus qhia rau engaging nrog persona. cov lus qhia suav nrog historically relevant lo lus nug mus ask, topics tus cwj pwm would find interesting, thiab cov lus qhia qhov ntawd lead mus deeper understanding. Zoo rau tub ntxhais kawm who need scaffolding los yog aren't sure yuav ua li cas mus begin historical interview.",
    "persona_submit_btn": "Xa koj cov xov mus persona tus cwj pwm. koj lo lus nug los yog response yog analyzed rau relevance thiab tob. AI persona yuav respond authentically based rau saum their historical context, knowledge, thiab personality. Well-crafted lo lus nug qhov ntawd qhia historical understanding earn bonus XP.",
